OL,6,FThen, through 2022 and 2023,
OL,7,Fskyrocketing inflation caused their
OL,8,Foperating costs to rise, while the
OL,9,Fcost-of-living crisis depressed sales.
OL,11,FThe number of pub closures increased
OL,12,Fto 80 per month over the first three
OL,13,Fmonths of 2024, up by 51% compared
OL,14,Fwith the same period last year,
OL,15,Faccording to official government data
OL,16,Ffor England and Wales.
