OL,3,CPub body calls for beer duty cut amid
OL,4,Cpotential outdoor smoking ban
OL,6,FIn August, Sir Keir Starmer said the
OL,7,Fgovernment would "take decisions" on a
OL,8,Fpotential outdoor smoking ban in an
OL,9,Feffort to curb preventable deaths and
OL,10,Falleviate pressures on the NHS.
OL,12,FIndustry leaders have warned that the
OL,13,Fproposed plans to ban outdoor smoking,
OL,14,Fincluding in beer gardens and outside
OL,15,Fstadiums, would be another "nail in
OL,16,Fthe coffin" for pubs and bars.
