OL,6,FOne of the BBPA's suggestions to
OL,7,Fcounter the impact on pubs is to
OL,8,Freform business rates, something which
OL,9,FLabour included in its pre-election
OL,10,Fmanifesto.
OL,12,FThe tax - which applies to non-
OL,13,Fresidential property such as pubs,
OL,14,Ffactories, shops and offices - has
OL,15,Fbeen criticised for unfairly punishing
OL,16,Fcompanies that trade in-person versus
OL,17,Fonline.
